again be dependent upon another power for its self defense... the rivalry
between the Terran Starfleet and the Shiratori Self-Defense Force is quite
notorious. (Shiratori was one of the first Terran colonies that grew big
enough to have colonial worlds of its own.  Hiroaki Nomura remarks "I
