between speakers of three main language groups:  Khalinghaarin, Selkeren,
and Kam\'zari.

I once ran a Traveller campaign set in this universe.  It was a lot of
fun.  Hiroaki ended up serving in the Kam\'zari House of Ataniell fleet
after being publicly disavowed by Shougun Rensselaer in order to avert a
full-scale war between Shiratori and Terra at a strategically inopportune
time...

Hm... maybe I should try that again.  Would any of you local SF Bay Area
people play in a heretic TU?

