Vilani BBQ debate, there just would be enough base level nutrients avalible
to really support a robust ecology.  It\'s why you let fields lie fallow,
soil needs to regenerate itself, which is a hideously complex and
precariously balanced act.  See "Dust Bowl"  Also, hydroponics tanks will
be pretty focussed on things that we can eat, which tend to not be that
great (after milenia of tampering) at adapting.

An interesting alternative my be to have various fungi take over the tanks,
and from there run rampant.  Ever see "Journey to the Center of the Earth"?
 Mushrooms make an excellent food source, and a great source for
interesting drugs and poisons.


