Heavy cavalry just means they have big horses (and usually big men ),
designed to charge into battle and use their impact against a holding
target. Whether the rider or mount is armoured is irrelevant

Light cavalry are designed for scouting and harrassing duties, including
mounted missile-fire, and are not normally expected to charge home against
enemy troops

