Heck, no ; Skinnerian operant conditioning is predicated on a \'black
box\' model of the brain. Most RW cognitive-behavioural therapies have
their origins in operant conditioning.
(My apologies to any psychologists or psychiatrists on the list who
were taught at schools with alternate views).

and :-

> If this technique makes a troublemaker stop being a troublemaker,
