thus the variance in interpretations.

The Zho nobles have decided what are appropriate avenues of expression
for proles, and make efforts to redirect the prole\'s interests and energies
into such avenues. A prole may be very active and dynamic, but all that
energy is carefully directed in directions that are harmless (or, more
