Last night I was thumbing through my GURPS Traveller books and for the 
"first" time noticed the 48-ton grav lifter in Far Trader. While designed to 
carry cargo containers at a starport, it has the lift to carry half the 
vehicles in Star Mercs.

I\'ve done some work on a larger, military version (GTL 10, 200 ton lift, 
enclosed two-man crew). It is actually cheaper than the 48-ton grav lifter 
(which is GTL 8). However, it has a very poor Health (6), even with the 
heaviest frame available (I may just have to add a large amount of empty 
space to make the body more robust).

