>about?  Likely it is some version of the Enigma, with some
>of The Push in it, right?  But vague categories don\'t help me
>very much.  I\'m asking for inspiration.


It depends. Adventures of the sort that you\'re talking about can be
mishandled and become merely "traditional" Traveller adventures. Horror
isn\'t in the plot, it\'s in the details.

Before I get to that, it is absolutely imperative that the GM is also a good
storyteller. I can\'t stress this enough. Nothing is worse than being in a
horror-themed campaign run by somebody who can\'t highlight the creepy parts
without sounding cheesy.

