skymelon vinyards in TTA). Regina has the Old Capitol, plus lots of
academic and educational resources (IMTU, U of Regina, Regni is one of the
largest, best equipped research facilities in the marches), plus all the
attractions of a major trade center. Regina is also still the Cultural
