the social circut on Mora starts on 002 and ends on 355... Commoners tend
to avoid it. Mora University is also a major bit. Depot/Spinward Marches is
known for displays on military history, plus the sector\'s Imperial Naval
Acadamy, with it\'s parades, airshows, and other pomp.

