Some American pacifists will allow you to kill them just because you want
to steal them blind.  I protested the reestablishment of the draft in the
US.  I believe in military service for those who choose it and that it is
honorable, I am not a conscientious objector, but I am opposed to
conscription especially in peacetime.  One of the pacifists I worked with
was arguing with someone who said-- what if I wanted to drag this little
lady off here and have some fun with her?  Pointing at me.

The guy said "She\'s not my property.  And I won\'t kill for any reason."

And I just thought, "well buster, if someone attacked you, I guess I won\'t
help you either and you better believe I won\'t sleep with you!"  Not that
I expect my lovers to defend me cuz I\'m a girl-- I\'d do the same for them.
I think that if you can\'t trust someone to protect you when you\'re
vulnerable you don\'t have much of a relationship regardless of your
gender.

I\'ve no problem with saying that willingness to commit suicide in an Asian
