    'body' => '  "Carlos Alos-Ferrer" <carlos.alos-ferrer@univie.ac.at> types out with his 
weasel powered keyboard:
 >> "Carlos Alos-Ferrer" <carlos.alos-ferrer@univie.ac.at> bangs out with his
 >toes:
 >> [snip]
 >>  >> >Does anyone have any firm anti-violence groups active in their
