>>Read "The Vang : the Military Form" (or "The Battlemaster")
>
>   In which case you let them call for help. As things develop, they
> may realize just what it is that they\'ve really asked for...
>
>   "Nuking the planetary surface is the only way to be sure..."

For a *slightly* less extreme problem, read Heinlein\'s "Puppet
Massters". Then transpose it to an out of the way world. Not only do
you have to stop this, you have to try to keep them from infecting any
one going offworld. 

In this case, the threat isn\'t enough to get the world nuked from
orbit. But it *is* enough to get a *strict* quarantine established. 

