    'date' => 'Sun, 14 Nov 1999 18:00:21  0900',
    'body' => '>Absolutely true. But I am thinking of Vilani megacorps rather than
>modern American companies. They will certainly have a different take on
>records storage.
>
>as for the first e-mail...it probably didn\' last long after being
>read...disk storage was mighty scarce in those days...
