Picture (or, as alternately known: Star Trek: The Motionless Picture, or
Star Trek: The Still[1]) was shot for the big screen. You\'re right that
there was a Star Trek television show that was in production around the time
that Star Wars came out, and you\'re right that the success of Star Wars
