correctly, even the *possibility* of a Star Trek II was in jeopardy as a
result of the critical and popular failure of the first film. TWOK is a
complete reversal of ST:TMP. There was lots of merchandise riding on the
first film that flopped as well. As an example, it took the Star Trek
franchise a hell of a long time to build up the credibility to start getting
toy makers interested again.
