>> ST:TMP was just a quickie job to get the fans to shut up.  Klingons
>> speaking Klingonese, long, loving pans over the Enterprise, characters
>> trickling in like some 23rd Century talk show.. (let\'s have a big hand for
>> Dr. McCoy, space hippie!)
>>
>> ST:TWoK was supposed to be the first Trek film, but Ricardo Montalban
>(sp?)
