Consider that the "World\'s Fair" runs for pretty much a year (or
more!). 

Allowing for travel time, and setup and the like, I\'d expect subsector
Fairs to run for at least a year. And say, have scheduled for starts 5
years apart. That\'s to allow travel & setup time for the exhibits from
worlds that can\'t afford to duplicate their setups. 

