kind of thing that Vargr raiding bands might do to extort cash from the
planetary government. It would be even more attractive because they probably
wouldn\'t have a Navy or Army to speak of.

Terror weapons would be most believable in the hands of Vargr (and the
Imperium for handling internal troubles, but I digress).
